      "content": "it's just that the \"value\" part feels like such a lie. like, if i went missing tomorrow, my boss would just hire a replacement in a week and my landlord would just rent the place to someone else. it's all just logistics. it feels like disappearing wouldn't even be a tragedy, just... a quiet way to finally get some peace from all this noise. don't you think it would just be easier for everyone if i just faded out?",
